headline: Growth Resources Draw Advisor with $110 Million to Ameriprise Financial from LPL
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, November 21, 2024--Ameriprise Financial, Inc. (NYSE: AMP) today announced that financial advisor Steve Salmon, MBA, recently joined the firm’s independent channel from LPL Financial with $110 million in assets. His office is located in Edina, Minnesota. Salmon was attracted to Ameriprise’s end-to-end support that helps advisors to deliver an outstanding client experience and grow their practice.
